    <title>Refugees contributor: Mohammed Khallouck</title>
    <description>Mohammed Khallouk is the second chairman of the Central Council of Muslims in Germany (ZMD). He is an expert in Islamic thought and politics, political Islam and intercultural dialogue between the West and the Islamic World. He was a lecturer in political science at Philipps-University of Marburg and at the University of German Federal Armed Forces Munich, and also served as Associated Professor for Islamic Studies at Qatar University, Doha.
</description>
